scenario: User successfully registers with valid information
Description: Verify that a new user can register with valid details
PreRequisities: User navigates to the registration page
TestSteps:
1. Enter valid user details
2. Click on the 'Register' button

scenario: Registered user logs in with valid credentials
Description: Ensure that a registered user can log in using correct credentials
PreRequisities: User is registered and on the login page
TestSteps:
1. Enter valid login credentials
2. Click on the 'Login' button

scenario: User adds a product to the shopping cart
Description: Validate that a user can add a product to their shopping cart
PreRequisities: User is logged in and viewing a product
TestSteps:
1. Click on the 'Add to Cart' button
2. View the shopping cart
ExpectedResult: Product is added to the cart

Description: Ensure that a user can successfully complete the checkout process
PreRequisities: User has products in the shopping cart
TestSteps:
1. Navigate to the checkout page
2. Enter shipping information
3. Complete the payment

scenario: User tracks the status of an order
Description: Verify that a user can track the status of a placed order
TestSteps:
1. Navigate to the order tracking page
2. Enter order details
3. View order status
ExpectedResult: User can see the current status of the order

Description: Ensure that an admin user can generate a sales report
TestSteps:
1. Navigate to the reporting section
2. Select date range and generate report

Description: Validate that a user can view the dashboard with relevant information
PreRequisities: User is logged in and on the dashboard page
TestSteps:
1. Navigate to the dashboard
2. View key performance indicators
ExpectedResult: User can see relevant dashboard information

Description: Validate that a user can change their account password
PreRequisities: User is logged in and on the account settings page
TestSteps:
1. Navigate to account settings
2. Enter current and new password
3. Save changes

Description: Ensure that an admin user can generate an analytics report
TestSteps:
1. Navigate to the analytics section
2. Select parameters and generate report
